---
export const prerender = true;
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | My Website" description="Learn more about me and this website.">
  <div class="prose mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">About</h1>
    <p>
      Welcome! This is a personal website built with <a href="https://astro.build">Astro</a>,
      styled with <a href="https://tailwindcss.com">Tailwind CSS</a>, and managed with
      <a href="https://tina.io">Tina CMS</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
      This site features a blog for sharing thoughts and tutorials, as well as an events
      calendar for keeping track of upcoming meetups, workshops, and conferences.
    </p>
    <h2>About This Site</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Built with Astro for fast, static-first performance</li>
      <li>Content managed through Tina CMS with Tina Cloud</li>
      <li>Dark mode support with system preference detection</li>
      <li>Deployed on Vercel with automatic builds</li>
      <li>RSS feed for blog subscribers</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Feel free to explore the blog and check out the upcoming events. If you'd like
      to get in touch, you can find me on social media.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
